longBusinessSummary: The Football Network (TFN) specializes in coverage of football. TFN produces a radio show, "TFN's Football Focus", which is carried on radio stations nationwide. The company is developing a 24-hour cable television channel devoted exclusively to football, providing coverage of the sport, its players, behind the scenes reports, and shows devoted to football-related topics. It has offices in Marina Del Rey, California and Lynnfield Massachusetts.
